summary: AN ORDINANCE amending and correcting Section 1 of Ordinance 113094 vacating a portion of THE ALLEY IN BLOCK 1, SUPPLEMENTARY PLAT OF FAIRVIEW HOMESTEAD ASSOCIATION FOR THE BENEFITS OF MECHANICS AND LABORERS, on the petition of the Seattle Times Company, and accepting a deed for street purposes and a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Comptroller File No. 293584).
